Description

The Tesla Model 3 is an all-electric sedan car produced by the American automaker Tesla. It is the company's most affordable model and is designed to offer a blend of performance, range, and affordability. The Model 3 features a minimalist interior with a large central touchscreen display, providing access to a range of features such as navigation, music, and climate control.

The car has a range of up to 263 miles on a single charge, making it ideal for both daily commuting and longer road trips. The Model 3 is also equipped with Tesla's Autopilot advanced safety and convenience features, including automatic emergency braking, adaptive cruise control, and lane departure warning.
